USE CASE: 14 produce a Capital city report containing the following columns: Name, Country, Population.

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context
As the organisation I would like to be able to produce a Capital city report containing the following columns: Name, Country, Population.

Scope
Company.

Level
Primary task.

Preconditions
Database contains names of countries, names of their capital cities and their populations.

Success End Condition
A report is available for the organisation to analyse.

Failed End Condition
No report is produced.

Primary Actor
Organisation

Trigger
A request for the data is made


EXTENSIONS
None.
SUB-VARIATIONS
None.

SCHEDULE
DUE DATE: Code review 2
